<div class="home-container">
    <div class="home-container-left col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-5 col-xl-4">

      <div class="home-header">
        <h1>Ruuuun, Forrest!
        Ruuuuuuuuuuun!</h1>
        <p>Tweet <span class="url-highlight"><i class="fas fa-hashtag"></i>runforrestrun</span> and Forrest Gump <br>will run another mile across America.</p>
        <div class="home-latest-tweets"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i> latest tweets</div>
      </div>

      <div class="home-tweet-container">
      <% @tweets.each do |tweet| %>
        <div class="tweet-container tweet-animation">
          <div class="tweet-avatar" style="background-image: url(<%= tweet.avatar %>) "></div>
          <div class="tweet-content">
            <div class="tweet-mile">
              <i class="fas fa-location-arrow"></i> <%= number_with_delimiter(tweet.mile, :delimiter => ',') %>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="tweet-flex">
                <div class="tweet-name">
                  <%= tweet.name %>&nbsp&nbsp
                </div>
                <div class="tweet-screen-name">
                  @<%= tweet.screen_name %>&nbsp&nbsp
                </div>
                <div class="tweet-date">
                  Â·&nbsp&nbsp<%= time_ago_in_words(tweet.date) %> ago
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tweet-message">
              <%= auto_link(tweet.message).html_safe %>
              <!-- <%= tweet.message %> -->
            </div>
            <% unless tweet.photo.blank? %>
            <div class="tweet-photo" style="background-image: url(<%= tweet.photo %>)"></div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="home-container-right col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-7 col-xl-8" id="map"
         data-markers=""
         data-mapbox-api-key="<%= ENV['MAPBOX_API_KEY'] %>">

       <div id="distance-counter"><i class="fas fa-location-arrow"></i> <span class="current-distance"><%= number_with_delimiter(@distance_remaining, :delimiter => ',') %></span> miles to go</div>

      <!-- launch about popup -->
      <button type="button" id="myBtn" class="home-about-btn" data-toggle="modal" data-target=".about-popup">
        <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> about
      </button>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- modal popup -->
<div id="myModal" class="modal">
  <div class="modal-content">
    <div class="modal-body">
      <div class="modal-split-left">
        <%= image_tag("run.gif", class: "modal-gif") %>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-split-right">

        <span class="modal-close">&times;</span>


        <div class="modal-forrest-icon"></div>

        <p>
          In 1979, Forrest Gump started running.
          <br>
          When he got tired, he slept.
          <br>
          When he got hungry, he ate.
          <br>
          When he had to go, you know, he went.
          <br>
          3 years, 2 months, 14 days, and 16 hours later, he stopped... and went home.
          <br>
          He'd run 13,089 miles.
          <br>
          <br>
          <span class="modal-bold">
          How long will it take Forrest (and the good people of the internet) to do it again?
          </span>
        </p>

        <a href="http://tristanviney.com" target="blank">
          <div class="modal-button">
            <i class="fas fa-bolt"></i> Built by Tristan
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
</div>
</div>
